The paper deals with safety guarantees for neural network systems, which is a topic related to control and system theory. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper addresses the verification of safety properties, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
